snippet.title: PINEAPPLE: A Bittersweet Revenge (Demo) - Gameplay video
snippet.description: An unconventional gaming adventure, PINEAPPLE combines a humorous storyline with delightful mini-games for an engaging experience This prank simulator weaves amusement, ease, and wit, unfolding a rib-tickling story about the quirks of bullying.
